td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>19th</td><td>+6</td><td>Ability Score Improvement (@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.oQVZcvQLB8Iwgv4d]{Bardic Versatility})</td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>20th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.mRfWrIW3rYylHgNA]{Magical Secrets (4)}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.BXA24py2g5rfCRoJ]{Superior Inspiration}</td><td>4</td><td>4</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr></tbody></table><h1>Bard Colleges</h1><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.rQnt6GKcnov3cT8o]{College of Creation}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.6XVjrWmRE4zXFBtt]{College of Eloquence}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.TbJa9eo5iej4P4I3]{College of Glamour}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.ZtrHRKouoTAoL49O]{College of Lore}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.UtSwzlZoa7tEl2fs]{College of Spirits}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.8wAzG98JbbX8HtCP]{College of Swords}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.pFgE4NvsvZVoEA8R]{College of Valor}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.5xSKN6l2NoV25a62]{College of Whispers}</p><h1>Multiclassing</h1><p>Should you wish to mulitclass into the bard, the prerequisites and proficiencies gained are listed below.</p><blockquote><h3>Bard Multiclassing Prerequisites</h3><p><strong>Ability Score Minimum:</strong> As a multiclass character, you must have at least an Charisma score of 13 to take a level in this class, or to take a level in another class if you are already a bard.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Bard Multiclassing Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Proficiencies Gained:</strong> If bard is not your initial class, here are the proficiencies you gain when you take your first level as a bard: light armor, one musical instrument of your choice, one skill from the class's skill lists.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Bard Multiclassing Spell Slots</h3><p><strong>Spell Slots</strong> Add your levels in the bard class to the appropriate levels from other classes to determine your available spell slots.</p></blockquote><p></p>",
